## Summary of Architectural Choices

| Aspect | Pattern |
|--------|---------|
| **Sub-component Export** | Named exports (not namespaced) |
| **Context** | React.createContext with explicit types |
| **State Tracking** | data-* attributes + Radix aria-* states |
| **Ref Forwarding** | Not used at wrapper level |
| **displayName** | Not used |
| **Styling** | CVA variants + cn() utility + Tailwind data-* selectors |
| **Orientation** | Explicit prop + data-orientation attribute |
| **Polymorphism** | asChild prop with Slot pattern |
| **CSS Classes** | `cn-{component}-{sub}` naming convention |

This architecture is **composition-focused**, **primitive-agnostic** (works with radix-ui or @base-ui/react), and **Tailwind-native** with no external CSS files.

